![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/410886d5-c55b-4db6-a54d-bbc10adaa72c/Screenshot_20240624_170212.jpg)

WWE RAW opens with Michael Cole announcing Pat McAfee didn't come into work and the Miz will be doing commentary instead.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ab25840c-4d44-4301-80ee-c6ae7d656607/Screenshot_20240624_170256.jpg)

Drew McIntyre inturrupts a recap of the Wyatt6 and shows a replay of what he did to CM Punk on SmackDown.

He prayed for this.. and the big man made it happen.. THE BIG MAN DREW MCINTYRE.

Drew hopes CM Punk is home being fed through a straw.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f9279db6-6bec-47a5-98fc-fa0838eedb26/Screenshot_20240624_170635.jpg)

Drew mocks CM Punk with the bracket he stole. He calls Larry ugly and says he’s going to win the Money in the Bank Ladder Match.

Drew says Punk wears this bracelet so he won’t feel alone. But now Drew wears this bracelet so DREW has CM Punk’s entire family by his side.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/ec3f5795-dec4-4fc0-8d98-6acbc4352ac2/Screenshot_20240624_172152.jpg)

*   ## **_BRON BREAKKER VS LUDWIG KAISER_** ENDS IN A NO CONTEST
    

Sheamus attacks Ludwig Kaiser and Breakker takes them all out for getting involved in his match again.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7701a7aa-becd-448e-b45f-b64439d3eddf/Screenshot_20240624_173131.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/59bfdbd0-a58c-4ac3-af23-ccda0c99d85b/Screenshot_20240624-173216_Chrome.jpg)

The Judgement Day are eating snacks they got from Liv Morgan when Damien Priest walks in and says they have to get rid of her. Carlito says she helped them win their match last week.

Dom shows a text he got from Liv. Damian asks how he's going to explain to Rhea where Liv got his number from. Dom says he doesn't know where she got it from

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/53aea521-b3e8-4cee-9065-cfc2287e6580/Screenshot_20240624_173926.jpg)

Bron Breakker vs Sami Zayn is official for Money in the Bank!!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/571f51f0-cdd7-4bfe-a5dc-f00261fe8db7/Screenshot_20240624_175139.jpg)

*   ## **_MONEY IN THE BANK QUALIFIER: VALKYRIA DEF. KAIRI SANE AND SHAYNA BASZLER_**
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d51e80f2-310a-4194-9037-22d97d87c91c/Screenshot_20240624_175200.jpg)

Drew McIntyre is demanding to be put into Money in the Bank automatically. But Adam Pearce says he’s been a disruption on both shows. He can’t be put into the match.

Drew says he’s going to show Adam the meaning of disruption.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/42f1a3a5-aa23-47f3-84df-cc0872c4c647/Screenshot_20240624_180046.jpg)

Liv Morgan asks Dom if he enjoyed the gifts and texts she sent him. She asks him to come out so she can give him another gift right here in front of all these people.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/3b096fe1-c45c-4a14-9fb7-83702538b9c7/Screenshot_20240624_180323.jpg)

Zelina Vega comes out instead and says Liv is busy chasing Dirty D while Zelina wants a title shot.

Liv says yeah, sure. Next week. Get outta here.. Oh Doooooomm..

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/bb4df461-1945-4c37-a827-94f7737b25c8/Screenshot_20240624_180535.jpg)

Dom comes out but the crowd won’t let him speak. Dom finally says he’s out to keep Zelina Vega from winning the title. Liv Morgan attacks Zelina Vega from Behind.

Rey Mysterio comes out to break up the brawl and Dom shoves Rey for touching Liv

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/8de13f1a-006a-4e5e-b130-60836ea81be4/Screenshot_20240624_181921.jpg)

Liv Morgan thanks Dom for being her hero against his deadbeat Dad tonight. Dom walks off.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f8f149c0-66c5-47a0-8af4-808b4fe52f06/Screenshot_20240624_181928.jpg)

R-Truth asks if that was Tom and Nick Mysterio who Liv is flirting with. R Truth loves, Love.

Liv says Truth can help her. She’ll go get Dom a match with Rey Mysterio next week and Truth can give a tag team Championship match to Finn Balor and JD McDonough.

Truth accepts because be always did like Carmella.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/473283fa-50a1-4c42-b1ea-10d0f442fda2/Screenshot_20240624_183242.jpg)

*   ## **_MITB QUALIFIERS: CHAD GABLE DEF. BRAUN STROWMAN AND BRONSON REED_**
    

Chad Gable wins a spot in the MITB when Abby the Witch comes out.

Chad Gable slips out of the ring before she could do anything to him.

The security guards by the announce table have their life ended and she hands Michael Cole a box.

Abby leaves.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9ebdd532-535e-4535-87c2-d555b6764e55/Screenshot_20240624_183437.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1bc9f809-d52f-44cd-b401-269f3de7715f/Screenshot_20240624_184109.jpg)

Michael Cole reveals a VHS tape in the box he was given by Abby the Witch.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e0e9599b-292e-4e63-ba13-9b037cd108f0/PhotoGrid_1_20240624184605.jpg)

FINALLY!!

Otis tells Chad Gable that he's glad he's ok but Chad Gable is NOT part of their family anymore.

Maxxine tells Gable she'll talk to Otis but they really are glad he’s ok.

The Creed Bros and Ivy Nile walk up.. Is Chad OK? He says no... He needs help.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5eaa3d18-1864-4c28-ae78-4038b663e397/Screenshot_20240624_184958.jpg)

*   ## **_ALBA FYRE AND ISLA DAWN DEF. KAYDEN CARTER AND KATANA CHANCE_**
    

Quick match. Damage CTRL lays out the Tag Champs after.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7d43e7ed-a67a-4891-af13-2b7ec9c387be/Screenshot_20240624_185219.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b866b4ca-19ac-4dec-ab8f-46694e92f819/Screenshot_20240624_185301.jpg)

Damian Priest catches Liv leaving the Clubhouse… But it’s not Dom she was with. It’s Finn Balor.

Finn says it’s not what it looks like. She was just there to say she got Dom a match with Rey Mysterio and she got Finn and JD a tag title match.

Finn says Liv is too good to be true. Priest agrees.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/65b5ad9e-07aa-4428-9e86-57ecdb1b5bc1/PhotoGrid_1_20240624192159.jpg)

Absolutely incredible segment here. WWE plays the VHS tape that Abby the Witch gave them.

It's Uncle Howdy interviewing Bo Dallas about the death of Bray Wyatt!

"Don't you think you're exploiting your brother's legacy?"

Bo Dallas says nobody could ever understand what he feels. What was he supposed to do? Let Bray Wyatt's legacy become a mossoleum??

Nothing will ever matter anymore. But the WYATT6 will never let them forget

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/f60187d6-ea42-4a9b-9bdd-8f4f5468a3f0/Screenshot_20240624_193248.jpg)

